@@@HOW CAN YOU GENERATE YOUR DISIRED VIDEO@@@

##SAMPLE PROMPT##
A slow cinematic pan inside a futuristic cybersecurity operations center, with glowing neon monitors
displaying streams of encrypted code, holographic interfaces floating in mid-air, and cybersecurity
analysts in dark clothing typing rapidly. The environment is illuminated with soft blue and purple neon
lighting, giving it a cyberpunk aesthetic. Outside the glass walls, a futuristic city skyline glows with tall
skyscrapers and flying cars in the night sky. Depth of field effect with sharp focus on the foreground and
blurred background city lights. The camera moves smoothly across the room, creating a dramatic,
professional look. Cinematic lighting, realistic details, slightly moody tone, 16:9 aspect ratio.


STEP 1: Decide on Your Core Elements
STEP 2: Add Visual Details !!IMPORTANT!!
STEP 3: Describe the Motion 
STEP 4: Define the Artistic Style / Quality
STEP 5: Put It All Together Clearly
Scene → Visual Elements → Motion → Style → Mood / Genre


!!PROMPT FORMULA FOR VIDEO!!
<u>Scene (What & Where) + Visual Details (Lighting, Objects) + Camera Movement + Action (if any) + Artistic Style + Mood<u>

-------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
*Scene (What & Where):               | A slow cinematic pan inside a futuristic cybersecurity operations center                                                                                                   |
-------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
*Visual Details (Lighting, Objects): | with glowing neon monitors displaying streams of encrypted code, holographic interfaces floating in mid-air, and cybersecurity analysts in dark clothing typing rapidly    |
-------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
*Visual Details (Lighting, Objects): | The environment is illuminated with soft blue and purple neon lighting, giving it a cyberpunk aesthetic                                                                    |
-------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
*Scene (What & Where):               | Outside the glass walls, a futuristic city skyline glows with tall skyscrapers and flying cars in the night sky                                                            |
-------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
*Visual Details (Lighting, Objects): | Depth of field effect with sharp focus on the foreground and blurred background city lights                                                                                |
-------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
*Camera Movement:                    | The camera moves smoothly across the room                                                                                                                                  |
-------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
*Action (if any):                    | cybersecurity analysts typing rapidly                                                                                                                                      |
-------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
*Artistic Style:                     | Cinematic lighting, realistic details                                                                                                                                      |
-------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
*Mood:                               | Slightly moody tone, cyberpunk, futuristic atmosphere                                                                                                                      |
-------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
*Scene Detail:                       | 16:9 aspect ratio                                                                                                                                                          |
-------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|

##SAMPLE PROMPT##
|*Corporate Cybersecurity Awareness Video*
A slow zoom-in on a serious cybersecurity expert sitting in a modern glass-walled office surrounded by
floating data visualizations and large digital maps of global cyber threats. Cool-toned lighting, clean tech
aesthetic, cinematic depth of field, professional corporate look.

*Sci-Fi Hacker Short Clip*
A shadowy figure in a hoodie typing on a glowing keyboard in a dark neon-lit room, surrounded by
holographic data streams and monitors. The camera slowly rotates around them as lines of code appear
floating in mid-air. Cyberpunk aesthetic, moody, atmospheric lighting, dramatic shadows.
